James is seeking a firewall exception from his IT department to serve webpages and Shiny apps from his Ubuntu server. The IT department has asked if James would be open to adding additional security agents such as Crowd Strike or Tenable. Assistant explains that these agents are cybersecurity platforms that can enhance server security but may impact performance and impose usage restrictions. James is advised to consider whether the benefits of enhanced security outweigh the potential inconveniences. Assistant suggests asking the IT department for more details about the specific impact on server functionality and work processes.
